{"tid":320814,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"大家幾歲開始有一種無力感","createTime":"2017-07-13T19:41:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-17T08:32:52.000Z","uid":54581,"like":33,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8404d126f50f04efaa63583a037b115814c7870a","tid":320814,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T19:41:55.000Z","msg":"以前，覺得努力有回報<br />\n<br />\n覺得搵幾皮野一個月已經叫叻仔，可以養妻活兒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n慢慢就發覺到 有啲野好難靠努力可以改變到<br />\n<br />\n你好努力讀書 做工程師 做醫生<br />\n搵幾皮至十皮野一個月<br />\n<br />\n點知原來個二世祖一個月零用錢都多過你<br />\n<br />\n點知原來靚仔靚女 唱歌做戲個批 彈起接個job又係你月薪"},{"pid":"2dce82745e4ddc9dca208f9b49f3531c927a894a","tid":320814,"uid":59569,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T19:42:55.000Z","msg":"知道女人係雞個陣"},{"pid":"0d6599f79acfe0b612d369015e19240201d994c7","tid":320814,"uid":46889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T19:43:16.000Z","msg":"16到<br />\n世界從來冇公平過 。"},{"pid":"fa23e8b1aeb5b1995991a767979596d80032fd55","tid":320814,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T19:54:13.000Z","msg":"無家底 無好好既資質 <br />\n--＞ 無能為力<br />\n--＞ 無自信<br />\n--＞ 想死<br />\n<br />\n樓主心路歷程"},{"pid":"258697ce7d35d41062bf76aeec987997784c87d2","tid":320814,"uid":42751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T19:55:36.000Z","msg":"搵萬幾嗰陣覺得好無力；到搵幾萬之後覺得好有希望"},{"pid":"ec46a05a2aab12768c0518a98a2520ef0a05e076","tid":320814,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T19:56:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e854ef3c7495952fb28280c46e5c7d5bf0e75813","tid":320814,"uid":27210,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T20:00:05.000Z","msg":"身體有事之後"},{"pid":"24c69bbfd1e9d0919b7cf60f68978c8ea31be79b","tid":320814,"uid":69791,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T20:01:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"56a558be66b03f78559ceb7aa6cfd3bb93e72d18","tid":320814,"uid":35388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"s